      <talk_question mid="95"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas${action:Talk}<BR>You should meet <FONT color=#a82424>Master Cleric Leonard</FONT>. <BR>He wishes to thank you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting-acceptted" mid="97" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>God's servant, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, at your service.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="96"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>Thank you for saving my priests…. <BR>They would have been in deep trouble if not for you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-1-a" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>God's servant, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, at your service.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>Thank you for saving my priests…. <BR>They would have been in deep trouble if not for you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-1-b" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Is there anything I can do?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>May the Goddess's grace be with you...<BR>Thanks to you the priests were saved, but they lost <FONT color=#a82424>something important</FONT>. I don't know what to do... Is this part of the Goddess's plan for us too?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-1-c" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>So what is the object that was lost?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>We were on a mission to deliver an <FONT color=#a82424>object</FONT> and we were on our way to <FONT color=#a82424>Mana Ridge</FONT>.<BR>The mission was top secret and we were very cautious, but the monsters somehow attacked the convoy and stole the <FONT color=#a82424>object</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-1-d" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>It's ok. I understand.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>Ah… I'm sorry.<BR>It's not that I don't trust you, but it is something that shouldn't be revealed. Please understand.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-1-d" image="QW_SaintHaven.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-1-e" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I was sent by the Archbishop.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>Thank you for understanding.<BR>However... What is a <FONT color=#a82424>Templar Knight</FONT> like you who should be protecting the <FONT color=#a82424>Saint Haven Cathedral</FONT> doing here?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-1-e" image="QN_SoceressCynthia.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-2" mid="88" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'll keep that in mind.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="87"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>By the order of the <FONT color=#a82424>Archbishop</FONT>... Hmm... I don't know what's going on but I hope you won't provoke the <FONT color=#a82424>sorceresses</FONT> of <FONT color=#a82424>Mana Ridge</FONT>. I heard that they still bear grudges about the clash between sorceresses and clerics that happened long ago.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-1" image="QN_Cl_Leonardo.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="89"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas${action:Talk}<BR>You should meet <FONT color=#a82424>Master Cleric Leonard</FONT>. <BR>He wishes to thank you.</html>]]></talk_question>
