      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-c" mid="104" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'll take it later.</HTML>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="102"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>Well, of course. You're new here. A <FONT color=#a82424>Basic Training</FONT> tutorial has been specially prepared so you can adapt well.<BR>Do you want to take the <FONT color=#a82424>tutorial</FONT> now?</html>]]></talk_question>
